<div class="netzwerk">
<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/><title>Netzwerk- und Internetkonfiguration</title><style>
</style></head><body><article id="28a57978-ca91-4fc4-b0c5-8e930ab96e30" class="page sans"><MudStack AlignItems="AlignItems.Center"><header><h1 class="page-title" onfocus="blur()"><strong>Netzwerk- und Internetkonfiguration</strong></h1><p class="page-description"></p></header><div class="page-body"><h2 id="d0142d85-6f4a-4212-995e-b6ef323a8c9b" class="">Einführung</h2><p id="b7c9b9b9-6a30-49b4-b90f-b23b8b30620d" class="">In diesem Kapitel lernen Sie die grundlegenden Konzepte und Befehle zur Konfiguration und Verwaltung von Netzwerk- und Internetverbindungen auf einem Linux-System kennen. Dazu gehören sowohl kabelgebundene als auch drahtlose Netzwerke.</p><h2 id="a8130506-3d12-4e8c-97f5-657aefdecc7a" class="">Netzwerkschnittstellen</h2><h3 id="631b6364-0e82-49cc-883e-069be286ddc9" class="">Arten von Netzwerkschnittstellen</h3><ul id="77e3c151-e598-4c1b-b6e8-32e22cbcc94c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Ethernet (kabelgebunden)</strong></li></ul><ul id="472e7f02-b5c9-4c55-a030-ac993cf462ad" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>WLAN (drahtlos)</strong></li></ul><ul id="1d9eb36d-5a4e-4d4e-84df-3085b6c2db2b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Loopback-Schnittstelle (localhost)</strong></li></ul><h3 id="f3ece6a9-894c-4436-9fe6-3667afae8649" class="">Anzeigen von Netzwerkschnittstellen</h3><p id="39e146cd-8e80-4145-9226-033264c187e9" class="">Um die aktuellen Netzwerkschnittstellen zu sehen, verwenden Sie den Befehl:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="6d3ab0f4-f0be-44a0-bfc2-f130fb268720" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">ip a</code></pre><p id="570c6fc2-1def-48e4-90a1-6855f84559d4" class="">oder</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="017a04c5-1162-45de-bcda-6d8ffcca9d20" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">ifconfig</code></pre><h2 id="27a55f42-5cd6-48d0-9f77-523ab2afaf72" class="">IP-Adressierung</h2><h3 id="fb73365c-e2d7-434a-8788-1e398ec65494" class="">Verständnis von IP-Adressen</h3><p id="9af22649-06bb-47ac-9420-ee9f1f516323" class="">Eine IP-Adresse ist eine eindeutige Kennung für ein Gerät im Netzwerk. Sie besteht aus vier Oktetten im Dezimalformat (IPv4) oder acht Gruppen von vier hexadezimalen Ziffern (IPv6).</p><h3 id="adcd6bdc-a9f4-4a2a-80a4-ad6c87df59b0" class="">Zuweisen einer statischen IP-Adresse</h3><p id="56b3d82f-3d60-4c85-8fe3-2d7ff9abde74" class="">Bearbeiten Sie die Konfigurationsdatei für die Netzwerkschnittstelle, z.B. <code>/etc/network/interfaces</code> für Debian-basierte Systeme oder erstellen Sie eine neue Konfiguration unter <code>/etc/systemd/network/</code> für systemd-basierte Systeme.</p><p id="a5157f4d-7937-418f-b58d-4eecd6a27536" class="">Beispiel für Debian:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="23585d78-7f7f-42d6-9146-6d37cd6e376c" class="code"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">auto eth0
iface eth0 inet static
  address 192.168.1.100
  netmask 255.255.255.0
  gateway 192.168.1.1
  dns-nameservers 8.8.8.8 8.8.4.4</code></pre><p id="b52b72d7-94d3-4321-9625-9bc284f29b52" class="">Starten Sie das Netzwerk neu:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="849de82a-70d8-4ce2-be7e-472d8a7c3153" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo systemctl restart networking</code></pre><h2 id="480816ad-55c3-48a7-8130-acc4467e831c" class="">DHCP-Konfiguration</h2><p id="ba1d58bc-0de2-4e06-8582-480a5c783570" class="">DHCP (Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol) weist Ihrem Gerät automatisch eine IP-Adresse zu. Um DHCP zu verwenden, konfigurieren Sie Ihre Schnittstelle wie folgt:</p><p id="6b8005db-af6e-41f0-9e55-17b211a06bd1" class="">Beispiel für Debian:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="06a6f7a2-fdf2-4210-a473-c5e1c575442c" class="code"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">auto eth0
iface eth0 inet dhcp</code></pre><p id="fe1300ab-8ec3-40b5-a457-d0a838994717" class="">Starten Sie das Netzwerk neu:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="38063b3b-dd99-46cb-90d6-f4124abd6358" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo systemctl restart networking</code></pre><h2 id="da19cbe1-6864-448a-b832-70ee77a644e8" class="">WLAN-Konfiguration</h2><h3 id="08528c5b-9456-4b9e-b1ad-fa43e7d06498" class="">Verfügbare Netzwerke anzeigen</h3><p id="35c3f859-7003-4119-bd1a-b22d0d0a0294" class="">Um verfügbare WLAN-Netzwerke zu scannen, verwenden Sie den Befehl:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="2fe7ce86-f95a-48dd-a732-3393ac53594d" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo iwlist wlan0 scan</code></pre><h3 id="4e2a577f-05b6-4317-b980-c3bbb13073da" class="">Verbindung zu einem WLAN-Netzwerk herstellen</h3><p id="6c4ca171-7671-4840-818b-c24f0821edde" class="">Bearbeiten Sie die Datei <code>/etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf</code>:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="78f8d396-b86d-4181-bebb-f9be5a5e3589" class="code"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">network={
    ssid=&quot;IhrNetzwerkName&quot;
    psk=&quot;IhrPasswort&quot;
}</code></pre><p id="268dfb15-9064-459c-8cc1-4c09288bd434" class="">Starten Sie den WLAN-Dienst neu:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="106dad75-9582-4ec9-98bc-1f558d53ecf1" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo wpa_supplicant -B -i wlan0 -c /etc/wpa_supplicant/wpa_supplicant.conf
sudo dhclient wlan0</code></pre><h2 id="e96c4072-c950-4720-8407-bdee8bbdd872" class="">Netzwerk-Tools</h2><h3 id="170b675f-8c75-494a-916c-cc3a85d5f8e6" class=""><code>ping</code></h3><p id="9286b9a5-ab2c-4a81-bd05-8bb07a06eabd" class="">Verwenden Sie <code>ping</code>, um die Erreichbarkeit eines Hosts zu überprüfen:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="88aa4bc2-3e90-4168-b2ab-c05bde51ccd4" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">ping example.com
</code></pre><h3 id="030800a5-c338-442b-8238-22155b69f5e7" class=""><code>traceroute</code></h3><p id="78ebf7b4-9b87-4919-aa0a-e025e29f7509" class="">Verfolgen Sie den Weg der Pakete zu einem Ziel:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="77d73acf-b62f-42a5-b549-822f7895af9d" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">traceroute example.com
</code></pre><h3 id="2fd2781f-4c2f-4aed-bbf4-20f3715a32e8" class=""><code>netstat</code></h3><p id="87edab1f-a0b1-46a4-a081-5a873c693726" class="">Zeigen Sie Netzwerkverbindungen, Routing-Tabellen und andere Netzwerkschnittstellen-Statistiken an:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="fad6a0a2-d848-44f5-a1dc-707a3573c688" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">netstat -tuln
</code></pre><h3 id="f0e769b7-53ec-4897-ab58-8965d031c647" class=""><code>nmtui</code> (NetworkManager Text User Interface)</h3><p id="319eed95-6798-4d74-824c-01b82362bac2" class="">Ein einfach zu bedienendes Tool zur Verwaltung von Netzwerkverbindungen:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="0a49050d-e190-441c-8846-45358187f7f0" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo nmtui
</code></pre><h2 id="e337d52e-5c50-4947-a9c8-509fe4b8e5c7" class="">Fehlersuche</h2><h3 id="12159c07-8821-4612-b547-a8a6aa67ce7c" class="">Verbindung überprüfen</h3><p id="17823008-4f08-4b9e-a7c5-1fae82a8cc68" class="">Stellen Sie sicher, dass Ihre Netzwerkschnittstellen aktiviert sind:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="ab5f47e8-8cc3-4dd2-b401-62a4031292a5" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo ip link set eth0 up
sudo ip link set wlan0 up
</code></pre><h3 id="19e64e7c-1b9c-4b5e-9718-6d537c4cde04" class="">DNS-Problembehebung</h3><p id="4ab00162-450e-42f3-a9df-540a2167bfdd" class="">Überprüfen Sie die DNS-Konfiguration:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="bf1adfd7-df8c-4b13-a862-71fda79631e3" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">cat /etc/resolv.conf
</code></pre><h3 id="d5280a84-7e47-43a2-a465-85e21f16db2d" class="">Firewall überprüfen</h3><p id="b1ce1a30-e32f-47ff-afd0-e0c0f5879a22" class="">Stellen Sie sicher, dass Ihre Firewall nicht den Netzwerkverkehr blockiert:</p><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="c4442158-b099-413d-8afc-fcca9516144a" class="code"><code class="language-Shell" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">sudo ufw status
</code></pre><h2 id="057296b7-313d-4185-8cf4-d4f7ab2bb78b" class="">Fazit</h2><p id="6907450c-f258-406d-b99f-67182b3b89c4" class="">Mit diesen grundlegenden Werkzeugen und Methoden sollten Sie in der Lage sein, Netzwerk- und Internetverbindungen auf einem Linux-System einzurichten und zu verwalten. Übung und Erfahrung werden Ihnen helfen, ein tieferes Verständnis zu entwickeln.</p><hr id="b5d4603b-025c-4f5d-bfcc-f1c62b9bb3da"/><p id="a4200ccb-163e-4a19-94ca-c58173540041" class="">Dieses Kapitel bietet eine gute Grundlage für Einsteiger in die Netzwerk- und Internetkonfiguration unter Linux. Ergänzen Sie es bei Bedarf um weiterführende Informationen oder spezifische Anweisungen für verschiedene Linux-Distributionen.</p></div></MudStack></article><span class="sans" style="font-size:14px;padding-top:2em"></span></body></html>
